line_1: But with all their hard running and riding,
line_2: For no one could tell tale or tiding,

line_1: Yet now desirous to be riding,
line_2: For new Events was still providing;

line_1: On his scaly back now riding,
Side by side as proudly riding,
line_2: This the force of Eirin hiding;

line_1: While this body of mine on its palfrey riding,
line_2: Right lazy of pace, or on smooth wave gliding,

line_1: Side by side as proudly riding,
line_2: This the force of Eirin hiding,

line_1: WHILE clouds on high are riding,
WHILE clouds on high are riding,
